reviews.text: Good quality traditional Cantonese light dishes in very reasonable prices. The set up is very old and looks like a greasy spoon. If you're into cost restaurant, opt to take out.

Had a pork liver & fish congee (豬潤魚片粥) and it was...delicious! The congee base was silky smooth, it came with 4 or 5 generous pieces of crunchy pork liver and big fatty fish belly at the bottom. It reminded me of the old fashioned home-made congee by my grandma. $35 was well-spent for my breakfast to start the day!
Cheap and good
Not bad.
It used to be my all time fav congee shop in HK now after 5 or 6 owners changing.........finally

result.name: 卓記粥店

reviews.text: 粥底👍🏻

幾年前，卓記粥店因為地鐵開通，租金飆升而傳出結業，心裏萬般不捨得。
因為已經多年，成為咗西環嘅地標。

好在，喺旁邊嘅街市，重新營業。
好開❤，試過之後感覺有少少變咗。

一段時間後，有人接手上址，繼續以同名營業。
開頭味道真係唔係咁接受到， 所以都放棄咗一段時間 。
加租減租，轉手幾次，本能嘅感覺，好似有多少點進步，而最近呢兩次食仲覺得有過之而無不及。
可能年紀大咗，條脷對味精，添加劑都會有啲抗拒。
難得呢兩次食完個艇仔粥，同埋腸粉炸兩都冇覺得口渴。
呢個感覺係好嘅，我都好欣賞，會做出咁嘅水準，希望佢哋繼續努力。
卓記-北街只頂用原先卓記的店名，其正店是在士美菲熟食市埸上，只開早午市。
出殯越嚟越差，老細冇心機做
Good quality traditional Cantonese light dishes in very reasonable prices. The set up is very old and looks like a greasy spoon. If you're into cost restaurant, opt to take out.
